room_title: Escape room "Dr. Frankenstein's Laboratory" by Excido Escape Room in Los Angeles
room_address: 6593 Collins Drive, Ste D 13  Moorpark, CA 93021
room_description: The Frankenstein family has been tinkering with life after death for generations, but this time, the experiment has gone horribly wrong. After successfully bringing a dead body back to life using modern technology, Dr. Frankenstein has been kidnapped by his creation. It is up to you, as the laboratory assistants to scour his lab and make the right serum that will bring the monster down. Time is of the essence - can you crack the genetic code that will save the doctor?
